# Google Drive encrypted backup (appDataFolder). The local file picker/backup
# works without these — they only enable Drive backup/restore.
# NOT secrets: VITE_* values ship in the client bundle. In Vercel set Sensitive = OFF.
#
# One shared app Client ID identifies the APP (type: Web application). Each user
# signs in with their own Google account; the backup lands in their private Drive
# appDataFolder. Enable the Google Drive API + add the drive.appdata scope on the
# OAuth consent screen. VITE_OAUTH_REDIRECT_URL points at the hosted
# oauth-redirect.html (only used by the future Android Custom-Tab flow).
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
VITE_OAUTH_REDIRECT_URL=
